const Notes = () => { return
  • Hide these notes
  • Commit events branch
  • Sleep diary needs to allow for offline access
  • What's up with our Internet?
  • Focus should go to first input box when I open a dialog
  • Health monitoring things:
    • Track last food
    • Track last drink
    • Track hunger in morning
    • Track number/length of nighttime awakenings
    • Reading check-in
      • Am I distracting?
      • What am I distracting from?
      • What am I feeling in my body?
      • What am I saying to myself?
    • Build some kind of report for items tracked.
  • Analyzer things:
    • Each interim block of time should trigger suggestions for things that might usefully be done in that time
    • Time after work should start with a status check: "I'm done", "I'm raring to go!", etc and then tailor suggestions accordingly
    • Track bedtime and time for prep and show available time after other events
    • Suggest todo items that will fit in time available
  • Tasks:
    • Do I have renters insurance currently?
    • Buy I bonds
    • Eye exam and new glasses
    • Dental checkup
    • Get yet another monitor mount so I can fix my desk space problem
  • Todo things:
    • If 'Shave' isn't checked off on a monday & wednesday, it should stick around for the next day and possibly not reappear within a day of being checked
    • Todo items should get repeating schedule?
    • "Refill pill containers" repeats every 10 days
    • "Pay rent" occurrs on the first of each month
    • Add estimated time to todo items
  • Event things:
    • Add link to Google calendar
    • Routine items should get filter for day of week
    • Perhaps I should be storing start & end times rather than start and duration?
  • Project things:
    • Project display should be a grid
    • Project items should have a button to create a related task
    • Checking off a task should add time to the related project
    • Should be able to download and restore projects
    • checkmarks should not remain on projects that have been checked
  • Track last food time from yesterday so that I can be informed today
  • Wierd bug: I can only load a type of data once unless I refresh
  • I would like to mark work as not showing, but instead show time between work and a scheduled event
  • Lots of things should follow the Project pattern
  • Today:
    • Sedgwick Money!!!
    • Thinky Test
    • Add button to projects to make related task
    • Reports from tracking data for Thursday
} // const clientId = "261912703565-hop0sl5u08fodcd9qvtd4vk2ha3rcc2d.apps.googleusercontent.com" // const apiKey = "AIzaSyBtTUouk4zCjNwrQMQov14i9Duj_JNS_Ec" export default Notes
